                    <p style="margin: 0in 0in 15pt; text-align: justify;"><strong><span style=" text-transform: uppercase;">DISCLAIMER OF INFORMATION OBTAINED ON THE SERVICE AND SOME USER SUPPLIED CONTENT</span></strong></p>
